    "## State: SERVICEABLE\n- **Description:** Build your bundle\n- **Triggers:**\n\t1. If you see 'Build your bundle'\n- **Actions:**\n\t1. DON'T DO ANYTHING, JUST TERMINATE AT THIS POINT\n- **End State:** serviceable_with_plans",
